%%%CALL -K1
%%%VALGRIND
%%%DESCRIPTION  -K1 without value.
%%%OUTPUT
ERROR in Fraud4 parameters. K1 value not provided after -K1
Run with the following arguments:
Fraud4 [-K1 <K1>] [-K2 <K2>] [-nr] [-o <classifiedDataset.dts>] <trainingDataset.dts> <testClassify.dts>

Parameters:
-K1 <K1>: an integer with the number of clusters to use in the reduction dimensionality algorithm (5 by default)
-K2 <K2>: an integer with the number of neighbouring instances to use in the KNN algoritm (6 by default)
-nr: Indicates that dimensionality reduction should not be applied in the clustering algorithm (by default dimensionality reduction is done)
[-o <classifiedDataset.dts>]: name of the file where the classified dataset will be saved (tests/output/output.dts by default)
<trainingDataset.dts>: name of the dataset file used as model (training dataset)
<testClassify.dts>: name of the dataset file to be classified (test dataset)
